<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
　　　　　　詠詩<lb />
<lb />
亡友南洲氏。風雲定<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ム</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">二</span></span>大是<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ヲ</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">一</span></span>。拂<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">テ</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">レ</span></span>衣<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ヲ</span></span>故山<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ニ</span></span>去<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ル</span></span>。胸襟淡<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">クシテ</span></span>如<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">シ</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">レ</span></span>水<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ノ</span></span>。悠然事<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">トス</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">二</span></span>躬耕<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ヲ</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">一</span></span>。嗚呼一高士。只<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ダ</span></span>道<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">フ</span></span>自<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ラ</span></span>居<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ルト</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">レ</span></span>正<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ニ</span></span>。豈<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ニ</span></span>意<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ハン</span></span>紊<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ルヲ</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">二</span></span>國紀<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ヲ</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">一</span></span>。不<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">リキ</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">レ</span></span>圖<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ラ</span></span>遭<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ヒ</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">二</span></span>世變<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ニ</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">一</span></span>。甘<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ジテ</span></span>受<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ントハ</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">二</span></span>賊名<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ノ</span></span><span change="gaiji" facs="../../../gaiji/2-88/2-88-57.png" rend="gaiji" rendition="img" source="※(「此／言」、第4水準2-88-57)" /><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ヲ</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">一</span></span>。笑<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">テ</span></span>擲<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">チ</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">二</span></span>此<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ノ</span></span>殘骸<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ヲ</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">一</span></span>。以<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">テ</span></span>付<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ス</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">二</span></span>數弟子<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ニ</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">一</span></span>。毀譽<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ハ</span></span>皆皮相。誰<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">カ</span></span>能<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ク</span></span>察<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">セン</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">二</span></span>微旨<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ヲ</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">一</span></span>。唯<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ダ</span></span>有<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">リ</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">二</span></span>精靈<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ノ</span></span>在<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ル</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">一</span></span>。千載存<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ス</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">二</span></span>知己<span rendition="small"><span rendition="sup">ヲ</span></span><span rendition="small"><span rendition="sub">一</span></span>。<lb />
　右詠南洲翁御話<lb />
　　　海舟散人<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
